io.atomix.core.multimap

Interface DistributedMultimap<K,V>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DistributedPrimitive, com.google.common.collect.Multimap<K,V>, SyncPrimitive

    public interface DistributedMultimap<K,V>
extends SyncPrimitive, com.google.common.collect.Multimap<K,V>
    This provides a synchronous version of the functionality provided by AsyncAtomicMultimap. Instead of returning futures this map blocks until the future completes then returns the result.
